-- Spain's Salgado Sees No Need for Portugal to Tap $1 Trillion Rescue Fund
-- B y   P a u l   T o b i n
-- 2010-11-26T13:54:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-26/spain-s-salgado-sees-no-need-for-portugal-to-tap-1-trillion-rescue-fund.html
Spain’s Finance Minister Elena
Salgado said she sees no need for Portugal to be rescued as
Spain’s neighbour has taken the needed measures. She spoke today
at a news conference in Madrid.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
